  "name": "Shroud of Flame",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You encircle yourself in an aura of protective flames. Each creature that hits you with an unarmed attack, Grapples you, or otherwise touches you takes @Damage[3[fire]] damage. When you Cast the Spell and the first time you sustain it each round, each creature in the area takes @Damage[3d6[fire]] damage (basic Reflex save).</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage caused by touching you increases by 1, and the fire damage when you Cast the Spell or sustain it increases by 1d6.</p>"
